text: Toto is the debut studio album by American rock band Toto and was released on October 15, 1978 through Columbia Records. It went to number 2 in Australia, number 5 in Sweden, number 8 in Germany, number 9 in Canada and the United States. It peaked at number 37 in the United Kingdom. == Track listing == == References == Category:1978 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Toto (band) albums
